<h3 id="buttons">Buttons</h3>

<p>Buttons are used with <a href="#template">template</a> messages. These button types are supported:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <a href="#url-button">URL</a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="#postback-button">Postback</a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="#call-button">Call</a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="#share-button">Share</a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="#buy-button">Buy</a>
  </li>
</ul>

<hr class="my-3">

<h4 id="url-button">URL button</h4>

<p>Compatible with Facebook Messenger's <a href="https://developers.facebook.com/docs/messenger-platform/send-api-reference/url-button">specification for the URL button</a>.</p>

<div class="card">
  <table class="table mb-0">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Property</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <i>type</i>
        </td>
        <td>
          <strong>string</strong> <span class="tag tag-success">Required</span>
          <p>Button type. Value must be <code>url</code>.</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <i>title</i>
        </td>
        <td>
          <strong>string</strong> <span class="tag tag-success">Required</span>
          <p>Button title</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <i>url</i>
        </td>
        <td>
          <strong>string</strong> <span class="tag tag-success">Required</span>
          <p>Button URL</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<pre>
{
  "type": "url",
  "title": "Dialog",
  "url": "http://dialoganalytics.com"
}</pre>

